20141203:
  AFFECTS: users of ports-mgmt/poudriere
  AUTHOR: bdrewery@FreeBSD.org

  Poudriere has been updated to 3.1.0. See the release notes at
  https://github.com/freebsd/poudriere/wiki/release_notes_31 for
