  to allow both vte and vte3 to be installed at the same time. To update
  after this change please do the following:

  # pkg_delete -f vte\*
   or
  # pkg delete -fg vte\*
   followed by
  # portmaster x11-toolkits/vte
   or
  # portupgrade x11-toolkits/vte

