20131125:
  AFFECTS: users of www/mod_wsgi
  AUTHOR: ohauer@FreeBSD.org

  The port www/mod_wsgi moved to www/mod_wsgi2 to reflect the port version.

  # portmaster -o www/mod_wsgi2 www/mod_wsgi
    or
