  Systemsimcell emulator now has a new dependency: x11-toolkits/linux-f10-blt.
  So you need to switch to linux-f10 ports in order to use 3.1.25 version.

20090828:
  AFFECTS: users of mail/dovecot and mail/dovecot-sieve
